1
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:14,020
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

2
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:17,580
ظآزSo let me fall with youظآز

3
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,420
ظآزAll the noise of the mortal worldظآز

4
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:24,060
ظآزIs nothing compared to her eyesظآز

5
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,180
ظآزWhoever said love itself is sinظآز

6
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,020
ظآزWhen a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlightظآز

7
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,180
ظآزPainting a banquet
of endless spring bloomsظآز

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 16=

11
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:50,640
Stop!

12
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,000
Stand down.

13
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,759
Yue Qin? It doesn't make sense.

14
00:00:56,079 --> 00:00:57,359
Why are you here?

15
00:00:59,159 --> 00:01:00,479
I want to go back to Zhao.

16
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,200
So,

17
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:07,400
you've also heard your father is dead.

18
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:10,319
Your brothers

19
00:01:10,599 --> 00:01:13,680
are killing each other
for the throne of Zhao.

20
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:17,319
I can help you return to Zhao.

21
00:01:17,799 --> 00:01:20,439
I can even help you claim the throne.

22
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:22,680
But first,

23
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,280
you must obey me.

24
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:27,159
Only then can I keep helping you

25
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:28,359
and Zhao.

26
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,560
The Emperor promised me

27
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,719
that if I worked for him,

28
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:38,879
he'd let me go home.

29
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,439
Mei Lin,

30
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,159
he also promised

31
00:01:44,159 --> 00:01:45,640
to send troops to make me the ruler.

32
00:01:46,079 --> 00:01:47,359
That's utterly foolish.

33
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,560
He has used you.

34
00:01:49,719 --> 00:01:50,920
To keep his throne,

35
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,159
he'll kill anyone,

36
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:53,439
even his own son!

37
00:01:53,719 --> 00:01:55,959
Why would he let you rule Zhao safely?

38
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:56,920
I know.

39
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,400
But all I want is to go home.

40
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:03,239
Only then can I think of anything else.

41
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:05,519
Mei Lin,

42
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,560
you have no home left.

43
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,879
Xichu is gone.

44
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:10,800
But I still have one.

45
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,719
My home is your home.

46
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,719
Let's go back to Zhao together.

47
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,800
I'll protect you. All right?

48
00:02:18,439 --> 00:02:19,240
Yue Qin,

49
00:02:20,199 --> 00:02:22,280
I thought we were the same.

50
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,520
I never expected

51
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,479
you'd join those palace monsters

52
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:27,199
who prey on others without mercy.

53
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,800
Yeah,

54
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,360
we are the same.

55
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,159
We're exactly alike!

56
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,159
Don't you want to go home?

57
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:39,520
As long as I can go home,

58
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,759
so what if I'm a monster?

59
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,879
Walking on thin ice,

60
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,680
at the mercy of others.

61
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,599
I've had enough of this life.

62
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:54,400
Mei Lin,

63
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,639
come with me.

64
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:59,120
I have no home!

65
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,159
All I have is revenge.

66
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,919
From now on, we're through.

67
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:10,039
I won't let your plan succeed.

68
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:15,919
Mei Lin!

69
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,840
Even you are abandoning me now?

70
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,599
Mei Lin.

71
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:38,960
Mei Lin!

72
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:40,280
Yu Sheng.

73
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,159
Yu Sheng!

74
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:42,879
Yes, Your Highness?

75
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:45,000
Send everyone to find Mei Lin!

76
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,800
I'm on it.

77
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:08,680
The letter was fake.

78
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:11,680
You forged Princess Anhe's handwriting

79
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,680
to lure me here.

80
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:14,639
Mr. Pei,

81
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,199
you're too upright.

82
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,680
Too clean.

83
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:21,120
The Emperor dislikes such purity.

84
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:25,319
And I need your head to trade

85
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:27,399
for my throne in Zhao.

86
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,920
You bowed to a tyrant,

87
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:32,920
becoming a lackey
for your own selfish gain.

88
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,439
Yue Qin,

89
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:35,600
you're nothing but

90
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,279
a disposable pawn to him.

91
00:04:38,759 --> 00:04:40,360
You don't need to tell me that.

92
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:42,480
From the very start,

93
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:46,160
all I ever wanted
was to be with Mei Lin.

94
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,639
Anyone who stands in my way

95
00:04:49,439 --> 00:04:51,360
will face nothing but death.

96
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,360
Pei Du!

97
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:13,260
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

98
00:05:13,510 --> 00:05:16,480
ظآزA celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edgeظآز

99
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:19,820
ظآزWings of light drift through the airظآز

100
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:23,500
ظآزLike blossoms that refuse to fadeظآز

101
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:27,300
ظآزIt asks no right or wrongظآز

102
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:30,300
ظآزNor fears the turning of fateظآز

103
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:33,020
ظآزA trace of spring on the windظآز

104
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:35,660
ظآزA whisper of a broken heartظآز

105
00:05:37,540 --> 00:05:39,620
ظآزA farewell song unfoldsظآز

106
00:05:39,900 --> 00:05:42,820
ظآزCarrying every sorrow within itظآز

107
00:05:43,220 --> 00:05:45,260
ظآزKarma weaves its endless threadظآز

108
00:05:45,380 --> 00:05:49,220
ظآزAnd I would follow you
without turning backظآز

109
00:05:49,700 --> 00:05:52,700
ظآزLife and death become
nothing sharp or finalظآز

110
00:05:53,020 --> 00:05:56,100
ظآزLove and hate are carried away
on the breezeظآز

111
00:05:56,700 --> 00:05:58,900
ظآزBefore freedom is ever reachedظآز

112
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:01,940
ظآزOne must first dissolve into tearsظآز

113
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:05,620
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

114
00:06:05,820 --> 00:06:08,940
ظآزSo let me fall with youظآز

115
00:06:09,140 --> 00:06:12,080
ظآزAll the noise of the mortal worldظآز

116
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:15,140
ظآزIs nothing compared to her eyesظآز

117
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:19,060
ظآزWhoever said love itself is sinظآز

118
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:22,700
ظآزWhen a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlightظآز

119
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:25,380
ظآزPainting a banquet
of endless spring bloomsظآز

120
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:28,340
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

121
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:32,700
ظآزTwo hearts leaning into one anotherظآز

122
00:06:34,260 --> 00:06:36,220
ظآزPerfectly, impossibly rightظآز
